## Homebrew (macOS / Linux)

```bash
brew tap {{HOMEBREW_TAP}}
brew install {{TOOL_NAME}}
```

## Go install

```bash
go install {{MODULE_PATH}}@latest
```

## Prebuilt binary

Download from [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/{{GITHUB_USER}}/{{TOOL_NAME}}/releases).
Available for macOS (amd64/arm64), Linux (amd64/arm64), Windows (amd64).

## Verify

```bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} version
```
